snippet.title: SAFEZONE VR Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the Official Announcement trailer for SafeZoneVR, 2 years in the making. A VR horror game coming soon free to side quest and pc vr. This immersive, ultra realistic game will make you live the storyline inside of this game.

Itch.io page: https://will-codes.itch.io/safe-zone
